### Frontend: Leaflet + OpenStreetMap Map

#### Install packages
```bash
npm install leaflet react-leaflet @types/leaflet
```

#### [NEW] [LeafletMap.tsx](file:///c:/Users/adhiy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/traffic%20engine/frontend/src/components/LeafletMap.tsx)

Replaces [GraphCanvas.tsx](file:///c:/Users/adhiy/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/traffic%20engine/frontend/src/components/GraphCanvas.tsx):
- `<MapContainer>` centered on T. Nagar, Chennai (13.045, 80.235)
- OpenStreetMap tile layer (free, no API key)
- Road edges as `<Polyline>` colored by traffic status (green/amber/red)
- Node intersections as small `<CircleMarker>`
- Ambulance markers (üöë icon, blue when available, orange when dispatched)
- Hospital markers (üè• icon)
- Emergency markers (‚ùó pulsing red icon)
- Animated path polyline for dispatch routes

